have been formed. Hundreds of thousands of volunteers are being formed. We can ensure risk reduction only from the coordination, cooperation, and assistance among all,\u201d the Home Minister added.\n\nOn the occasion, Minister Thapa inaugurated the exhibition on Earthquake Safety Digital.\n\nDuring the event, the Chief Executive Officer of the National Reconstruction Authority (NRA) Sushil Gyawali shared the progress made by the NRA in the reconstruction of the properties damaged by the Gorkha Earthquake.","title":"Home Minister seeks firm commitment to safeguard lives from earthquakes - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/15/156486/","video":[]}
